dc_title_s: China veteribus sinarum regio nunc incolis tame dicta; Guilielmus et Johannes Blaeu.
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Includes decorative cartouche and dedication to Theodoro Bas. 1 map: hand col.; 40 x 49 cm This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
